    "text": "This key displays a label, likely on a button or panel, indicating information related to an agent. It appears within a list of options, and the label will show \"Agent info\" if the item is an AI agent; otherwise, it displays \"Room info.\" Translators should consider this key as part of a UI element presenting information about either an agent or a room.",
